{
  "info": {
    "name": "Suara Rumah API - Dummy Testing Kit",
    "description": "Import ini ke Postman, jalanin request dari atas ke bawah urut. TIDAK butuh header auth apa pun -- device diidentifikasi cukup lewat variable 'device_id' (default 'test-device').\n\nGanti variable 'base_url' kalau backend-nya ga di localhost.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://127.0.0.1:8000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "device_id", "value": "test-device", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "alert_id", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0. Health Check",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": [""] }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "1. Setup Device (opsional)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register Device (opsional, ga wajib dipanggil)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/devices/register", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["devices", "register"] },
            "description": "Endpoint ini masih ada tapi opsional -- ga ada endpoint lain yang cek api_key hasilnya lagi. Boleh dilewatin, langsung pakai device_id bebas (default variable 'test-device')."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Set Emergency Contact (dummy nomor)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"contact_number\": \"+628123456789\"\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/devices/{{device_id}}/contact", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["devices", "{{device_id}}", "contact"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Emergency Contact",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/devices/{{device_id}}/contact", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["devices", "{{device_id}}", "contact"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Kirim Fitur Suara (RMS/ZCR/Peak)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Predict Features - contoh NORMAL",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"device_id\": \"{{device_id}}\",\n  \"rms\": 0.02,\n  \"zcr\": 0.03,\n  \"peak\": 0.1\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/predict-features", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["predict-features"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Predict Features - contoh CRASH (match screenshot)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"device_id\": \"{{device_id}}\",\n  \"rms\": 0.041,\n  \"zcr\": 0.054,\n  \"peak\": 1.0,\n  \"latitude\": -0.502106,\n  \"longitude\": 117.155594\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/predict-features", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["predict-features"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Predict Features - contoh KDRT #1 (belum eskalasi)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"device_id\": \"{{device_id}}\",\n  \"rms\": 0.3,\n  \"zcr\": 0.2,\n  \"peak\": 0.95\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/predict-features", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["predict-features"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Predict Features - contoh KDRT #2 (TRIGGER eskalasi+alert)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (data.alert_id) { pm.collectionVariables.set('alert_id', data.alert_id); console.log('alert_id ke-simpan:', data.alert_id); }",
                  "pm.test('escalating harus true (2 anomali dalam 30 detik)', () => pm.expect(data.escalating).to.eql(true));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"device_id\": \"{{device_id}}\",\n  \"rms\": 0.35,\n  \"zcr\": 0.25,\n  \"peak\": 0.9\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/predict-features", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["predict-features"] },
            "description": "PENTING: jalanin request ini SEGERA setelah 'KDRT #1' (dalam 30 detik) biar window tracking ngitung 2 anomali beruntun -> escalating jadi true -> alert WA ke-trigger (atau muncul warning 'credential belum diisi' di server log kalau Twilio belum di-setup)."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Baca Data (buat dashboard app)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Latest Reading",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/devices/{{device_id}}/latest", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["devices", "{{device_id}}", "latest"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Alert History",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/devices/{{device_id}}/alerts?limit=20",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["devices", "{{device_id}}", "alerts"],
              "query": [{ "key": "limit", "value": "20" }]
            },
            "description": "Kalau ini balikin 500 + 'query requires an index', klik link di error message Firestore-nya sekali aja (butuh index composite user_id+timestamp), tunggu 1-2 menit, lalu ulangi."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "4. Follow-up Alert",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Confirm Safe (tandai alarm palsu)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/alerts/{{alert_id}}/confirm-safe", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["alerts", "{{alert_id}}", "confirm-safe"] },
            "description": "alert_id otomatis kesimpan dari response 'KDRT #2' di atas (kalau alert beneran ke-trigger)."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "5. Endpoint Lama (upload audio/teks langsung, di luar arsitektur resmi mobile)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Predict dari Teks (dummy)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"text\": \"aku bunuh kamu kalau macam-macam\",\n  \"user_id\": \"test-user\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/predict-text", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["predict-text"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Predict dari Audio Upload (pilih file dari folder 'Data sound kdrt' manual)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [{ "key": "file", "type": "file", "src": [] }]
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/predict", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["predict"] },
            "description": "Di tab Body, klik field 'file', pilih salah satu .MP3 dari 'Data sound kdrt/high confident/' atau 'Data sound kdrt/low confident/' di project."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
